* "Timing" or "Choreography" panel, for continuous actions (UI similar to GarageBand's tracks)
* Starting inventory (for ctrl-shift-N)
* 'Always visible in map' flag for lines and polygons
* 'Visible in HUD' flag for lines, polygons, text, and objects
* Map appearance for lines, polygons, text, and objects
* Line flags to block enemies, allies, players, and teams
* Modifier key in texture mode to adjust dx and dy
